description: GodEats services supposed to help adults and minors to find out if particular food or food item is healthy or no. The data used in GoodEats is acquired from open contents and GoodEats services is not responsible for accuracy of the data. The answers, provided by GoodEats should not be used as rule or diet and common sense shall be always applied when following the answers that the application is providing. If you have special condition, you should consult with your doctor. Keep in mind that some food items that are healthy for one person, can be harmful for another (allergies, special diets, genetical and acquired diseases).
exampleInteractions: Alexa ask Good Eats Is broccoli healthy
Alexa ask Good Eats are brussels sprouts healthy
Alexa ask Good Eats is french fries good for you
name: Good Eats
shortDescription: Service that helps people to find out if food is healthy or no.
